flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 59: Vendor Catalog Publish and Moderation Pipeline

  Submit[Vendor submits product listing]
  Validate[Validate required fields\nimages/video/brand claims]
  PolicyScan[Policy and counterfeit signal scan]
  Flagged{Flagged for moderation?}

  AutoPublish[Auto-publish listing]
  Queue[content_moderation_queue enqueue]
  Review[Moderator review]
  Decision{Approved by moderation?}

  Publish[Publish to catalog]
  Index[Update Meilisearch + semantic index]
  Reject[Reject listing with reason]
  FixLoop[Vendor correction and resubmission]
  Escalate[Escalate to compliance takedown path]

  Submit --> Validate --> PolicyScan --> Flagged
  Flagged -- No --> AutoPublish --> Index
  Flagged -- Yes --> Queue --> Review --> Decision

  Decision -- Yes --> Publish --> Index
  Decision -- No --> Reject --> FixLoop --> Submit
  Review -->|Severe counterfeit risk| Escalate
